  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: \r\n\r\n1. No confirmation when switching to Mainnet\r\n2. App closes when i try to login after switch\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\n1. I should have confirmation message that i am going to switch to Mainnet\r\n2. App should not close\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n1. No confirmation when switching to Mainnet\r\n2. App closes when i try to login after switch\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status (Ropsten RPC)\r\n- Go to networks\r\n- Tap **Mainnet**\r\n- Tap connect\r\n- Pay attention that no confirmation is shown\r\n- Tap account name to login and provide password\r\n- Tap sign in\r\n- Pay attention that status is closed after that\r\n\r\nNOTE: when doing the same steps but switching to **Mainnet with RPC** - user is logged in immediately, no additional log in step, no app close.\r\n\r\nPoint to discuss with design team, cc @denis-sharypin \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: nightly 244 \r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS",
